{"name": "odoo14-addon-delivery-carrier-preference", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-delivery-carrier-preference", "version": "14.0.1.1.3", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/wms", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-product-total-weight-from-packaging", "odoo14-addon-sale-stock-available-to-promise-release", "odoo14-addon-stock-picking-group-by-partner-by-carrier", "odoo"], "summary": "Advanced selection of preferred shipping methods", "upload_time": 1734528285}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fwms-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/wms\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/wms/tree/14.0/delivery_carrier_preference\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/wms-14-0/wms-14-0-delivery_carrier_preference\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/wms&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Delivery Carrier Preference\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:bf790f15e174c79cdf29fac8a7a93364e37a09610b3360390db3f25d17de70f5\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows to define preferred shipping methods in order to fine tune\nthe selection of proper delivery carrier from delivery operations according to\nthe quantity available to promise.\n\nMoreover it provides the possibility to force the recomputation of preferred\ndelivery carrier on the release of operations for Delivery Orders.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nGo to Inventory > Configuration > Delivery > Preferred Shipping Methods to\ndefine new Preferred Shipping Methods.\n\nA Preferred Shipping Method can either define a specific Delivery Method or\nuse the partner's defined Delivery Method.\n\nThese Preferred Shipping Methods will then be filtered out according to the\npicking's estimated shipping weight.\n\nEstimated shipping weight calculation relies on `product_total_weight_from_packaging`,\ni.e. packaging weight if defined, with a fallback on product weight and uses\nthe quantity available to promise only.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/wms/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/wms/issues/new?body=module:%20delivery_carrier_preference%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Akim Juillerat \\<<mailto:akim.juillerat@camptocamp.com>>\n\nTrobz\n\n- Dung Tran \\<<mailto:dungtd@trobz.com>>\n- Khoi Vo \\<<mailto:khoivha@trobz.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Camptocamp\n\nThe migration of this module from 13.0 to 14.0 was financially supported by Camptocamp\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/wms](https://github.com/OCA/wms/tree/14.0/delivery_carrier_preference) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models.stock_location_route", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models.stock_location_route.StockLocationRoute", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models.stock_location_route.StockLocationRoute._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models.stock_location_route.StockLocationRoute.force_recompute_preferred_carrier_on_release", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models.delivery_carrier_preference", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.delivery_carrier_preference.models..delivery_carrier_preference", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.del